text:
Well... first,
Which sushi should I start with...

? What's wrong, Asahi? Why aren't you eating?
There are lots of delicious sushi going around.

Producer-san,
Please take a look at this part of the menu.

...Oh, you get bonuses for eating sushi.
Which ones do you want?
Of course, I want all of them!

Huh!? There are three types,
so that's at least 21 plates!?

That's not the issue...
Wait...? Is that not the issue...?

Oh, here comes the sushi!
I'm going to eat a lot~!
